    "desc": "GWI is the consumer data your marketing needs. Our insights and analytics help you understand what your consumers want and how to target them.  GWI features digital insight data from countries all around the world, helping you generate ideas and measure impact.",
    "navbar": "GWI.\nOur platform\nOur data\nResources\nPricing\nAbout\nSign in\nFree demo",
    "text": "Cookies\nWe use cookies to make sure your experience on our site is the best it can be. If you'd like to opt out or customise that experience, click on Manage my cookies \nRead our privacy policy\nManage my cookies\nAccept all\nGWI.\nOur platform\nOur data\nResources\nPricing\nAbout\nSign in\nFree demo\nYour audience is in this platform\nOur platform gives you instant access to the answers you’re missing. With consistent audience research that’s run worldwide, this is your window into their world – through a global and local lens.\nFind out more\nLearn how people around the world think, act, and feel\nOur harmonized audience data represents 2.7 billion digital consumers, so you’re always on top of what’s happening with up-to-the-moment insights.\nTake a look\nStay ahead of the pack\nMake better decisions with better data. Fine-tune your understanding of the biggest trends in a whole new way with the latest reports, infographics and trusted insights from the experts.\nSee our resources\nDig deeper with rich data\nNo one should know your audience better than you. Drive real growth and enhance your strategy with insights that are easily understood and widely shareable.\nFind out more\nDiscover the trends that’ll dominate 2023\nYou need to know the top consumer trends for the year ahead, we’ve got the full story. Connecting the dots digs deep into the data, so you’re one step ahead of your competitors and even closer to your customers.\nSee the future\nWhat makes us different?\nWe’re obsessed with providing actionable insights that let the numbers tell the full story.\nUnderstand any audience instantly\nWe’re on a mission to help you make better decisions with better data\n0\nmarkets\nWe’re here to help you stay tapped into emerging trends. Get a top-level look at your global audience or zero in on local regions.\n0k+\nbrands\nWe put noteworthy brands on center stage. Discover what makes them tick from perceptions and engagement to ownership and more.\n0B+\nconsumers\nIt’s in our DNA to leave no stone unturned. Every year we interview more than a million people with the world’s biggest survey.\n0k+\nprofiling points\nOur platform helps you figure out your audience like an expert. Dive deep to analyze their interests, behaviors and values down to the detail.\nWe know who\nGet the full story behind the campaign, and find out who cares about the stuff that matters.\nSee more\nYou’re in good company\nDiscover why some of the world’s most influential agencies and brands rely on GWI.\nWe use GWI for every single pitch.\nMcCann Worldgroup\nDon’t take our word for it\nWe love sharing in our customers’ success, and they love sharing their stories. Read case studies from agencies, brands, publishers and businesses of every shape and size to find out how they drive real growth with our solutions.\nCase study\nMatching brands to the right partners (and proving the ROI)\nCase study\nBoosting post interactions by 7,616%\nCase study\nDriving 41k revenue in the first month\nCase study\nEnhancing campaign performance by 88%\nShow me more\nBack to top\nHaven’t found what you’re looking for?\nLook below for more information about our data, platform and how we help brands outperform the competition.\nProducts\nGWI Core\nGWI Gaming\nGWI Kids\nGWI Sports\nGWI USA\nGWI Work\nGWI Zeitgeist\nGWI Travel\nCustom services\nTV reach and frequency\nResources\nBlog\nCase studies\nReports\nWebinars\n2022 trends\nCoronavirus research\nGen Z\nGWI\nAbout\nData coverage\nCareers\nPartnerships\nContact\nGWI Accelerator\nGWI Student\nPress center\nMore\nTerms and conditions\nPrivacy\nCalifornia residents\nHelp\nGet in touch\n+44 (0) 207 731 1614\nhello@gwi.com\nFollow us\nFacebook\nTwitter\nLinkedIn\nInstagram\nYouTube\nGWI.\nCopyright © GWI 2022. All rights reserved.",
